list.name: Changes
list.comment: The Circle code refactored to its own class "Zone" and added customized map by including mapId to the activity_map layout file. At the time of the commit the customized map does not appear due to unknown reasons, possibly related to google cloud being slow to update.

task.summary: Implemented google maps api, permission handling for location, automated location updates and camera movement to follow user location. Commit intentionally missing gradle.properties file to prevent API key from being exposed.

Added a feature where initial position of the user is fetched independent of the continuous location updates. The location is then used to draw a circle near the user that is randomized to be within a specified range from the user.

The Circle code refactored to its own class "Zone" and added customized map by including mapId to the activity_map layout file. At the time of the commit the customized map does not appear due to unknown reasons, possibly related to google cloud being slow to update.
